text: The Samsung Galaxy Note 10 and Samsung Galaxy Note 10+ (shortened to Note 10 and Note 10+, respectively) are Android smartphones produced by Samsung Electronics as part of the Samsung Galaxy Note series. The Samsung Galaxy Note 10 and Galaxy Note 10+ were unveiled on 7 August 2019 and next to the Samsung Galaxy Note 9, with a North American release on 23 August 2019 and international rollout throughout August and September. ==Related pages== * Samsung Galaxy Note Category:Samsung Galaxy Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2019 Category:Mobile phones with multiple rear cameras Category:Mobile phones with 4K video recording
title: Samsung Galaxy Note 10
